name: Artisanica
description:
Use with Automatic1111 or InvokeAi on RunDiffusion where you can generate your favorite CIVITAI models.

I was carefully picking models, that are realistic, beautiful, well trained, popular and sales safe. This is how Artisanica has happened and so far I am satisfied with the merge.

Artisanica is focused on realism but is able to do some painting stuff, it should create also very beautiful environments and details of the created image.

And I will be happy to see what you create with Artisanica, hope you will enjoy the use!

Artisanica is a child of this beautiful parents:

  • Dreamshaper (dreamshaper_5BakedVae)

  • Deliberate (deliberate_v2)

  • Real Elden Apocalypse (realeldenapocalypse_Analogsexknoll)

  • Realistic Vision (realisticVisionV20_v20)

  • Liberty (liberty_main)

  • RPG (rpg_V4)

Thanks to all wonderful creators and mergers of previous models!!! <3

NOTE: if you find that the prompts below look "familiar" it's because I've taken them from other reviews and models here, to basically compare my model to other examples. Credits to the original authors. Thanks for the benchmark.
